Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libcassandra2 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Apache Cassandra & DataStax Products client driver- development files
 A modern, feature-rich, and highly tunable C/C++ client library for Apache
 Cassandra and DataStax Products using Cassandra's native protocol and
 Cassandra Query Language along with extensions for DataStax Products.

